 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bthedruidsgrove.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=kolnar>Kolnar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#333399>(4/4/01 5:10:27 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovespells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2261.topic&index=17>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> ack</span><hr size=1> Reading this, I feel that my specialize: evoc is useless.  I thought so for some time, but now I see.  My question is, and don't flame me too hard, what can I do to change over to alteration?  I use nukes rarely now, and I blew it by choosing that in the first place.<br>
